{"word":"H3510 - כָּאַב - kâʼab - kaw-ab' - Grieving - வருத்தமான","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>כָּאַב"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kâʼab"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kaw-ab'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Grieving / வருத்தமான"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - துக்கமாயிரு, துயரமாயிரு, சஞ்சலப்படு, நோவிரு, கெடு, காயப்படு, நோவுண்டாக்கு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to be in pain, to be sore, to have pain, to be sorrowful"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to be in pain (physical)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"2) to be in pain (mental)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Hiphil)"},{"paragraph":"1) to cause pain, to hurt, to mar"},{"paragraph":"2) pain, mar (participle)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to feel <i>pain</i>; by implication to <i>grieve</i>; figuratively to <i>spoil: - </i>grieving, mar, have pain, make sad (sore), (be) sorrowful."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3510 - כָּאַב - kâʼab - kaw-ab'/3510\">H3510</a>, <a href=\"#/H3511 - כְּאֵב - kᵉʼêb - keh-abe'/3511\">H3511</a>, <a href=\"#/H4341 - מַכְאֹב - makʼôb - mak-obe'/4341\">H4341</a>"}]}